12.short_description: Delivery Chat for medium sized cities LatAm

18.description:
igo is next-generation delivery on-demand chat technology.

Helps retailers in Latam's mid-sized cities to increase their operational capacity by enabling them to connect to their social networks and receive orders in an automated way through a super chatbot. In addition to mapping the best routes for on-demand deliveries.

igo was founded in 2020, at COVID-19 by Sarita Garcia, @Gustavo Lizarazo and Ruben Hincapie, to help businesses survive their new reality: using the usual platforms and optimizing deliveries improving their sales. This led them to build Mylla, a chatbot that receives, organizes and assigns requests, for businesses in intermediate cities that are underserved by the big platforms. Today igo is working to expand to 2 Latin American countries by 2022.

"Retailers have been able to multiply their sales by 3.5X in just two months of adaptation. Something that used to take them about 8 to 12 months, with igo they achieve it faster because we free them from logistical weaknesses and use the tools that they and their customers know best.  Already more than 100 stores in two cities do it with igo, which is only 2% of the market we can reach," said Ruben Hincapie, co-founder and CEO of igo.

This new reality has accelerated the demand for delivery services not only in capital cities but also in the intermediate cities where igo is focused. The challenge is to provide businesses with more channels to receive orders, making it simpler and more habitual. Can you imagine not only being able to connect with your brand friend, but also being able to order your transport and buy in your favorite e-commerce with just one click?  So you can say: "I want a hamburger" or "I need to get to work" and in less than 15 minutes, someone will do it for you?

12.short_description: No bank account? No problem? Use Whizmo to send money, pay bills, pay in store and online. Your money. Your rules. Your freedom

18.description:
Welcome to Whizmo which is revolutionising the way people manage their finances. We offer a wide range of financial services including international remittance, bill payments, in-store contactless payments, and local peer-to-peer transactions, all accessible to everyone, regardless of whether they have a bank account or not.

With our international remittance service, you can send money to anyone in the world quickly and securely, without the need for a bank account. We offer competitive exchange rates and low transaction fees, ensuring that you get the best value for your money.

Our bill payment service allows you to pay your bills with ease, even if you don't have a bank account. Whether it's your electricity, water, or phone bills, you can make payments through our app and avoid the hassle of waiting in line or dealing with cash.

With our in-store contactless payment feature, you can make purchases at any participating merchant without the need for cash or a bank account. Simply scan the QR code, and you're done! It's instant, easy, and secure.

Finally, our local peer-to-peer transaction service allows you to transfer funds to anyone within your community, even if they don't have a bank account. Whether you're splitting a meal with friends or paying for a service, you can easily and securely transfer funds through our app.

Our fintech application is designed to be accessible and easy to use, even for those without a bank account. We believe that everyone should have access to financial services, and our app makes that possible. Try it out today and experience the convenience and security of modern finance!

Storydots helps to bridge this gap, integrating into online stores’ carts allowing customers to mark a purchase as a gift. The store also benefits from that, getting invaluable data to boost new sales.
